'''Ari Lahti''' (born 1963) is a Finnish businessman and the owner of [[KuPS]] of the [[Veikkausliiga]]. He is the founder, owner, and chairman of [[Helsinki]]-based [[Ice Capital]]. He was formerly employed at the [[Bank of Finland]], and was born in [[Leppävirta]].<ref>http://www.hs.fi/urheilu/a1435899434165 Lahti Summary</ref>

