'''Robin Chan Yau-hing, [[Grand Bauhinia Medal|GBM]], [[Gold Bauhinia Star|GBS]], JP''' (born 1929, [[Chaoyang, Shantou|Chiuyang, Swatow, Kwangtung, Republic of China]]) also known as '''Chen Youqing''' ({{zh|c=陳有慶}}; {{lang-th|ขี่เห่ง แซ่ตั้ง}}; {{RTGS|''Khi-heng Sae-tang''}}), or '''Rabin Sophonpanich''' ({{lang-th|ระบิล โสภณพนิช}}; {{RTGS|''Rabin Sophonphanit''}}) is the eldest son of [[Chin Sophonpanich]] (founder and former president of [[Bangkok Bank]]), and serves as the [[Chairman]] of the [[Asia Financial Group]].<ref>[http://www.asia-financial.com Asia Financial Group website]</ref> He has two son, [[Stephen Tan]] & [[Bernard Charnwut Chan|Bernard Chan]], who are [[Executive Director]] and [[President]] of the [[Asia Financial Group]] and its main subsidiary, Asia Insurance respectively.

